### **Smart Contracts**
```solidity
// Framework
- Hardhat (preferred) o Foundry
- Solidity 0.8.20+
- OpenZeppelin Contracts 5.0

// Testing
- Hardhat Tests (Chai/Mocha)
- Hardhat Gas Reporter
- Solidity Coverage

// Security
- Slither
- Mythril
- OpenZeppelin Defender (monitoring)
```

### **Frontend**
```javascript
// Core
- React 18
- TypeScript
- Vite (build tool)

// UI Library
- shadcn/ui (Tailwind-based)
- Radix UI primitives
- Lucide icons

// Web3
- ethers.js 6.x
- Mezo SDK
- wagmi (optional)

// State Management
- Zustand o Jotai (lightweight)
- React Query (server state)

// Utils
- date-fns
- recharts (graphs)
- framer-motion (animations)
```

### **Backend (Optional)**
```javascript
// Si necesitas backend para yield aggregation
- Node.js + Express
- TypeScript
- Prisma (DB ORM)
- PostgreSQL

// Cron Jobs
- node-cron (yield checks)
```

### **Infrastructure**
```yaml
# Deployment
- Vercel/Netlify (frontend)
- Heroku/Railway (backend opcional)
- IPFS (descentralized hosting opcional)

# Monitoring
- Tenderly (smart contract monitoring)
- Sentry (error tracking)

